{"id": 2285, "genre": 1000, "title": "理想状况下，你觉得一个即将踏入社会的人最应该知道哪些东西?", "description": "人们常常抱怨还没准备好就从象牙塔里出来了，究竟怎样才算准备好了，一个人进入公共生活前应该具备哪些基本的储备？（题图来自：istock）", "record_count": 36176, "comment_count": 66, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180416165349vPuaeqb4hYILtoNT.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-04-22T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4035, "title": "理想状况下，你觉得一个即将踏入社会的人最应该知道哪些东西?", "content": "理想状况下，你觉得一个即将踏入社会的人最应该知道哪些东西?", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 276029, "content": "能分得清美丑，但不把自己的审美强加给别人", "image": "img/option/option/201804161717345bV91ihn7S04UoOl.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 276030, "content": "了解法律常识，也可以讨论更合理法规的可能", "image": "img/option/option/20180416171842BUNSrefuwODa2YiT.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 276031, "content": "能阅读也知道在哪阅读严肃新闻，愿意了解正在发生什么", "image": "img/option/option/20180416171943A7LsNm4dIrMSfuFW.gif", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 276041, "content": "明白历史“不唯一”，愿意去了解和接受不同的历史观和“历史真相”", "image": "img/option/option/20180416173133uOCd1K8j3I2AcEJ0.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 276042, "content": "有基本的生理和性常识，不把性和下流划等号", "image": "img/option/option/20180416173239tmPh4bfduK5DaBnx.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 276043, "content": "知道基本的公共道德，但不站在道德高地去要求别人", "image": "img/option/option/20180416173316BoOzyXAvWI0GUj6T.gif", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 276045, "content": "知道事物有“本质内核”，能思考和讨论一些哲学问题", "image": "img/option/option/20180416173505bI7np1WvdeQ8SJxs.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 276046, "content": "明白文化的多样，会尝试理解和包容其他国家/地域/民族的文化", "image": "img/option/option/20180416173627tv7VP2uYRFLodmKx.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 276050, "content": "知道所在领域里都有哪些“伟人”、已有的行业标杆在哪里", "image": "img/option/option/201804161737390NHgzFj5ylOvVCMt.gif", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 277219, "content": "明白语言的重要性，会利用不同的语言去拓展更多世界", "image": "img/option/option/201804212348532DMljHYQsdgmnfqa.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}